window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Leaving fame and fortune behind, it's the ultimate escape.... </p> <p>Can you live on love alone?</p> <p>Willow Carruthers - British Oscar winner, style icon and mother of three - is facing a crisis: she’s broke, discovery of her partner’s infidelity has left her a single mother and, if the banks have their way, she’s about to be homeless.</p> <p>Meanwhile, Kitty - nanny to Willow’s children - is desperate to keep her job and knows just the place they can retreat to: her crumbling ancestral home in the Bristol countryside, Middlemist House.</p> <p>To both women in their hour of need, the idea of leaving LA seems brilliant in theory. That is, until Kitty’s brother, Merritt, returns home unannounced….</p> <p>From London to LA, <i>The Perfect Retreat</i> is pure escapism - full of sex, scandal and intrigue.</p>"; 
